  "title": "A sparkling bean-like UFO was spotted in Porto Alegre-RS [1995]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/30/a-sparkling-bean-like-ufo-was-spotted-in-porto-alegre-rs-1995/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1jt",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 20th, 1995</strong>. Time: 18h15. Duration: 30 seconds. When walking on a cottage in the region of Porto Alegre, State of Rio Grande do Sul, three people spotted &#8220;a sparkling, half-rounded, bean-like object&#8221; of white color flying at high speed. According to witnesses, the UFO was flying on a straight trajectory towards the south at high altitude, and was observed with the naked eye in a clear sky of a sunny afternoon.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.393. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Porto Alegre, Estado do Rio Grande do Sul”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
